VMy work is about the behaviors that we all engage in unconsciously,
p4
aVon a collective level.
p5
aVAnd what I mean by that, it's the behaviors
p6
aVthat we're in denial about,
p7
aVand the ones that operate below the surface of our daily awareness.
p8
aVAnd as individuals, we all do these things, all the time, everyday.
p9
aVIt's like when you're mean to your wife
p10
aVbecause you're mad at somebody else.
p11
aVOr when you drink a little too much at a party, just out of anxiety.
p12
aVOr when you overeat because your feelings are hurt, or whatever.
p13
aVAnd when we do these kind of things,
p14
aVwhen 300 million people do unconscious behaviors,
p15
aVthen it can add up to a catastrophic consequence
p16
aVthat nobody wants, and no one intended.
p17
aVAnd that's what I look at with my photographic work.
